=head1 DESCRIPTION

Specifies the type of message that triggers a bot.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> StandardMessages => Str

Sets standard messages as the bot trigger. For standard messages:

=over

=item *

C<ALL>: The bot processes all standard messages.

=item *

C<AUTO>: The bot responds to ALL messages when the channel has one
other non-hidden member, and responds to MENTIONS when the channel has
more than one other non-hidden member.

=item *

C<MENTIONS>: The bot processes all standard messages that have a
message attribute with C<CHIME.mentions> and a value of the bot ARN.

=item *

C<NONE>: The bot processes no standard messages.

=back



=head2 B<REQUIRED> TargetedMessages => Str

Sets targeted messages as the bot trigger. For targeted messages:

=over

=item *

C<ALL>: The bot processes all C<TargetedMessages> sent to it. The bot
then responds with a targeted message back to the sender.

=item *

C<NONE>: The bot processes no targeted messages.

=back




